<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-89-0749 </DOCNO><TEXT>This paper describes a practical scheme for Automatic Generation Controlincluding Reserve Monitoring which is proposed for introduction in theNetherlands in the coming years. With the aim of further minimizing productioncosts and to improve control action a centralized control structure hasbeen worked out. When designing the scheme special attention has beenpaid to relative simplicity for purposes of controllable developmentcosts and the practical use in power system operation.</TEXT></DOC>